  <name>LinkForge</name>
  <summary>Create and inspect symbolic links and hard links</summary>
  <developer id="io.github.morningfrog">
    <name>MorningFrog</name>
  </developer>
  <description>
    <p>
      LinkForge is a desktop and command-line tool for creating, inspecting,
      and managing symbolic links and hard links.
    </p>
    <p>
      It supports direct link creation, same-file checks, hard-link counts,
      sibling discovery, hard-link group scanning, hard-link-preserving
      directory clones, and batch link creation.
    </p>
  </description>
